divs: Sighting Detailsat the end of my driveway taking the dog out. saw these lights moving without any sound. the cluster of 4 eventually dimmed out as they mover to the right. the single light remained lit a little longer. the event lasted 5-10 min. very strange as there was no sound and it was a quiet night.
